author: Daniel Greene
description:
I’ve finally met my match — The Invader’s Plan by L. Ron Hubbard. This sci-fi novel didn’t just challenge my patience… it freakin broke it.

From incomprehensible prose to uncomfortable themes and a story that somehow manages to do everything wrong, this is the first book in my life that I could not finish. In this video, I take you through the unhinged journey that is The Invader’s Plan — and why I had to put it down for good.
